Hello,
Below is a list of T3 Turkey Reds available for sale.  The Ungraded cards have a ‘grade’ noted which is simply my estimate of what PSA might assign.  

In addition, if anyone is looking for more difficult cards or variations I have some of those too.  For instance Doolin, a few no-ad backs and some very difficult front/back combinations.  Please inquire. 

PM me or send an email to [url]craigdiamondt3@yahoo.com[/url] if you’d like photos or have any questions. Thanks. 

Happy collecting,
Craig
